  "commentary": "**DEALER HEDGING COMMENTARY:**\n\nWith SPX at 6766.74 sitting right in the heart of massive negative gamma between 6750-6765 (both showing -50M+ amplifying walls), dealers are forced to buy this rally and will accelerate any move higher toward the 6800 positive gamma wall where they'll turn into sellers. The BREAKOUT regime with -62B total GEX means dealers are short gamma and providing momentum fuel - they're buying strength here but will hit the brakes hard at 6800. Watch for violent whipsaws around the 6750-6765 cluster if we reverse, as dealers will flip to aggressive selling on any dip back into these levels.\n\n**Bottom line:** expect a fast move up to 6800 where selling pressure kicks in, or violent selling if we break back below 6765.",
